---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Complete Guide to Hair Salon Marketing Automation in Canada" description="Fill your chairs, reduce no-shows, and build client loyalty without spending all day on your phone.">
  <article class="py-12 md:py-20">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
      <!-- Back Link -->
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto mb-8">
        <a href="/industries/salons-spas/hair-salons" class="inline-flex items-center text-sky-600 hover:text-sky-700 dark:text-sky-300 font-medium">
          <svg class="w-4 h-4 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 19l-7-7 7-7"></path></svg>
          Back to Hair Salons
        </a>
      </div>
      
      <header class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center mb-12">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-4 mb-6">
          <span class="bg-pink-100 text-pink-700 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-medium">Hair Salons</span>
          <span class="text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 text-sm">10 min read</span>
        </div>
        <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-6">
          The Complete Guide to Hair Salon Marketing Automation
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300 mb-8">
          Fill your chairs, reduce no-shows, and build client loyalty without spending all day on your phone.
        </p>
      </header>

      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <div class="prose prose-lg prose-slate dark:prose-invert max-w-none">
          
          <p class="lead text-xl text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 mb-8">
            Hair salons have a unique challenge: you deliver transformations, but empty chairs and no-shows destroy your revenue. Automation changes the math entirely.
          </p>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mt-12 mb-4">No-Shows Are Revenue Killers</h2>

          <p>
            Every empty chair is money you'll never get back. Automated confirmation texts and day-before reminders cut no-shows dramatically—without your front desk making dozens of calls.
          </p>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mt-12 mb-4">The 6-Week Color Reminder</h2>

          <p>
            Your color clients need touch-ups every 6-8 weeks. But life gets busy and they forget. Automated "time for your next color" messages at the perfect interval keep chairs full and clients gorgeous.
          </p>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mt-12 mb-4">Build Salon Loyalty, Not Stylist Loyalty</h2>

          <p>
            When clients feel connected to your salon—through birthday messages, VIP recognition, loyalty rewards—they stay even if their stylist leaves. Build relationships that survive staff changes.
          </p>

          <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-pink-600 to-fuchsia-600 p-8 rounded-xl text-white my-12">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-white">Ready to Fill Your Chairs?</h3>
            <p class="text-pink-100 mb-6">
              Get a free consultation and see exactly how we'd automate your bookings, reminders, and rebooking.
            </p>
            <a href="/contact" class="inline-flex items-center bg-white dark:bg-slate-900 text-pink-600 px-6 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-800 transition">
              Book Your Free Demo
            </a>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </article>
</Layout>
